						<name>Cleisson Vieira Raimundi</name>
					
					
						<email>cleisson.raimundi@gmail.com</email>
					
					
				</author>
			
			<summary>If you need them, &lt;em&gt;Feeling Responsive&lt;/em&gt; offers you a breadcrumb navigation. You can easily turn it on/off via frontmatter.</summary>
			<content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/feeling-responsive/design/breadcrumb/">&lt;!--more--&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;alert-box alert &quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;WARNING: If you use breadcrumbs be aware, that if you use categories, you need pages for those categories. If not, the link in the breadcrumb won’t work.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;front-matter-code&quot;&gt;Front Matter Code&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;highlighter-rouge&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;code&gt;breadcrumb: true
&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</content>

			
